title: jellyfin
description: * [DockerHub jellyfin](https://hub.docker.com/r/jellyfin/jellyfin) * [Docs](https://jellyfin.org/docs/) ### Ports * 8096/tcp is used by default for HTTP traffic. You can change this in the dashboard. * 8920/tcp is used by default for HTTPS traffic. You can change this in the dashboard. * 1900/udp is used for service auto-discovery. This is not configurable. * 7359/udp is also used for auto-discovery. This is not configurable.
